                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="bg-[rgb(21,101,192)] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Endodoncia</span>
                  <span class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">1 – 2 sesiones</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Accordion Item 2 -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-[rgb(33,33,33)] text-lg font-bold">Quiero dientes más blancos</h3>
                <svg class="accordion-chevron w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-content hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  Las manchas por café, vino o tabaco van acumulándose en el esmalte con el tiempo. El blanqueamiento profesional actúa en profundidad y los resultados son visibles desde la primera sesión.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="bg-[rgb(21,101,192)] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Blanqueamiento dental</span>
                  <span class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">1 – 2 sesiones</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Accordion Item 3 -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-[rgb(33,33,33)] text-lg font-bold">Tengo dientes chuecos</h3>
                <svg class="accordion-chevron w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-content hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  La mala alineación afecta tanto la estética como la función masticatoria y puede causar desgaste desigual. Con brackets o alineadores transparentes logramos resultados progresivos y duraderos.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="bg-[rgb(21,101,192)] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Ortodoncia</span>
                  <span class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">6 – 18 meses</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Accordion Item 4 -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-[rgb(33,33,33)] text-lg font-bold">Perdí una pieza dental</h3>
                <svg class="accordion-chevron w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-content hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  La pérdida de una pieza afecta la masticación, el habla y puede provocar desplazamiento de los dientes vecinos. Los implantes son la solución más permanente y de apariencia más natural disponible.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="bg-[rgb(21,101,192)] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Implantes dentales</span>
                  <span class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">3 – 6 meses</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Accordion Item 5 -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-[rgb(33,33,33)] text-lg font-bold">Aprieto los dientes de noche</h3>
                <svg class="accordion-chevron w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-content hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  El bruxismo desgasta el esmalte de forma irreversible y genera dolores de cabeza y mandíbula. Una guarda dental a medida protege tus piezas mientras duermes y alivia la tensión muscular.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="bg-[rgb(21,101,192)] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Protección dental</span>
                  <span class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">1 cita + entrega</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Accordion Item 6 -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <h3 class="text-[rgb(33,33,33)] text-lg font-bold">Solo quiero prevención</h3>
                <svg class="accordion-chevron w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="accordion-content hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  La revisión y limpieza periódica es la forma más efectiva y económica de evitar tratamientos costosos en el futuro. Detectamos problemas antes de que se vuelvan mayores.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="bg-[rgb(21,101,192)] text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">Limpieza dental</span>
                  <span class="border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">45 – 60 min</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function () {
  // Bind accordion triggers
  document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-trigger').forEach(function (trigger) {
    trigger.addEventListener('click', function () {
      const content = this.nextElementSibling;
      const chevron = this.querySelector('.accordion-chevron');
      const isOpen = !content.classList.contains('hidden');
      
      // Close all other accordions
      document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-content').forEach(function (otherContent) {
        if (otherContent !== content) {
          otherContent.classList.add('hidden');
          const otherChevron = otherContent.previousElementSibling.querySelector('.accordion-chevron');
          otherChevron.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        }
      });
      
      // Toggle current accordion
      if (isOpen) {
        content.classList.add('hidden');
        chevron.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
      } else {
        content.classList.remove('hidden');
        chevron.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
      }
    });
  });
})();
</script>